title: WTF | Watch: This dog has gone mega-viral with his special way of getting off a narrow ledge
text:
When there's nowhere to go but down, a dog's gotta do what a dog's gotta do.
Tango and his backwards shuffle has as of now been viewed by over 12.5 million people after his video was posted on Facebook. Expect his own Twitter, Instagram and web series any day now.
All we can think of is this .
